en-US:
MonkeyPaste is a clipboard manager, automation and productivity tool like no other. Enhancing your clipboard into an enriched and organized part of your workflow,
featuring an intuitive and low-profile interface that supports text, files and images. Designed for flexibility, with an ever-growing community-driven libray of plugins.

It began as an experiment by a programmer wanting more than just copy and paste out of the clipboard. He wanted a simple command like Control+C that would 'add to' instead 
of 'replace' what was on the clipboard. And the experiment worked, eureka! The little tool was very handy. This entrigued the programmer with more ideas and more experiments, that 
now has become "MonkeyPaste". 

As the desktop is to your files, MonkeyPaste intends to be to your clipboard. Its a suite of tools carefully designed to seemlessly integrate and interoperate with 
any application or format of content. Control+C and Control+V are much more than just shortcuts. They are the ports of entry all applications share, carrying a 
wealth of value and meaning you deserve to have available at your fingertips. Not just thrown away after the next Control+C.

I am that programmer mentioned earlier and I want everyone to be able to find use out of MonkeyPaste. So it and all of its features are completely free to use. 
I also want you to feel comfortable using it. So I assure you, as being the only force behind its creation, that NONE of the (very) personal information that can arise on 
your clipboard is ever tracked or stored ANYWHERE beyond your own machine. Period.
Initial Release
MonkeyPaste

The clipboard is a jungle. MonkeyPaste is the KING! Swing from app to app, copying this and pasting that like never before with MonkeyPaste!! A brand-new, cutting edge clipboard and analytic automation tool!!!
Thomas Kefauver

en-US: â— Simple and friendly interface with both horizontal/vertical layouts, list/grid view and multi-monitor support
â— Both light & dark themes are completely dynamic, use any color you want
â— Integrated help & hints right in the interface. Online manual, videos and forum to get you started all on the website (monkeypaste.com/docs)
â— Optimized for performance and stressed tested with 1,000,000s of clips.
â— Anytime search, just start typing using both simple & advanced filtering on clips and their sources over dozens of fields
â— Organize your clips in tag trees and create resusable filters
â— Safe, secure and private local data storage (no data collection) always encrypted with optional 2-factor password protection and easily block apps or websites from your tracker

en-US: â— Extensive drag-and-drop support, custom global shortcuts, routing and mouse-free navigation
â— Custom mouse modes: right-click paste and left-click auto-copy
â— Append mode: Copying becomes 'add to' instead of 'replace' on the clipboard. Both text and files, fully customizable
â— Sophisticated clip tracking, sources and usage with enhanced support for Firefox and Chromium-based browsers (Chrome, Edge, Brave)
â— Fully-featured clip editor with rich text (tables, lists, links, etc.) with find/replace and highlighting
â— Store your images in the secure database, ready to use as files anytime on-demand just drag-and-drop!
â— Powerful text templating for quick, dynamic pasting from your snippet collection
â— Trigger & Action designer for custom automations and action chaining
